<plot>A Docu-drama exploring the events leading up to the attempted kidnapping of Princess Anne in 1974 by schizophrenic loner Ian Ball. The programme looks at Ball's life leading up to the fateful day and dramatizes the fateful evening in which he shot 4 people before being arrested. The action is inter-cut with interviews with the surviving participants.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?609849</url></doc>
